### CSS Text Decoration

**text-decoration** adds decorative lines to text.

---

### Decoration Line

```css
text-decoration-line: underline;      /* Line below */
text-decoration-line: overline;       /* Line above */
text-decoration-line: line-through;   /* Line through middle */
text-decoration-line: underline overline; /* Multiple */
text-decoration-line: none;           /* Remove decoration */
```

---

### Decoration Style

```css
text-decoration-style: solid;    /* Default */
text-decoration-style: double;
text-decoration-style: dotted;
text-decoration-style: dashed;
text-decoration-style: wavy;
```

---

### Decoration Color

```css
text-decoration-color: red;
text-decoration-color: currentColor; /* Same as text color */
```

---

### Decoration Thickness

```css
text-decoration-thickness: 2px;
text-decoration-thickness: 0.1em;
text-decoration-thickness: auto;  /* Default */
```

---

### Shorthand

```css
/* line style color thickness */
text-decoration: underline wavy red 2px;
text-decoration: underline;
text-decoration: line-through dotted blue;
```

---

### Common Uses

```css
/* Remove link underline */
a {
  text-decoration: none;
}

/* Show underline on hover */
a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

/* Strikethrough for deleted text */
del {
  text-decoration: line-through;
}

/* Fancy heading */
h1 {
  text-decoration: overline underline double #333 3px;
}
```

---

### text-underline-offset

Controls the gap between text and underline:

```css
a {
  text-underline-offset: 4px;
}
```

---

### text-underline-position

```css
text-underline-position: under;  /* Below descenders */
text-underline-position: auto;   /* Browser default */
```

> **Best Practice:** Use `text-decoration: none` on links, then add underline on `:hover` for interactive feedback.
